## SOLID Principles

### Single Responsibility

```php
// ❌ DON'T - Class doing too much
class Game
{
    public function save() {}
    public function validate() {}
    public function sendNotification() {}
    public function generateReport() {}
}

// ✅ DO - Separate responsibilities
class Game
{
    public function save() {}
}

class GameValidator
{
    public function validate(Game $game): bool {}
}

class GameNotificationService
{
    public function notify(Game $game): void {}
}

class GameReportGenerator
{
    public function generate(Game $game): Report {}
}
```

### Open/Closed Principle

```php
// ✅ DO - Open for extension, closed for modification
interface ScoreCalculator
{
    public function calculate(Game $game): int;
}

class StandardScoreCalculator implements ScoreCalculator
{
    public function calculate(Game $game): int
    {
        return $game->points;
    }
}

class BonusScoreCalculator implements ScoreCalculator
{
    public function calculate(Game $game): int
    {
        return $game->points * 2;
    }
}
```

### Dependency Inversion

```php
// ✅ DO - Depend on abstractions, not concretions
interface GameRepository
{
    public function find(int $id): ?Game;
}

class EloquentGameRepository implements GameRepository
{
    public function find(int $id): ?Game
    {
        return Game::find($id);
    }
}

class GameService
{
    public function __construct(
        private readonly GameRepository $repository
    ) {}
}
```

