public function store(StoreGameRequest $request)
{
    $validated = $request->validated();
    $game = Game::create($validated);
}

// ❌ DON'T - Trust user input
public function store(Request $request)
{
    $game = Game::create($request->all());
}
```

### Output Escaping

```blade
{{-- ✅ DO - Auto-escape (default) --}}
<p>{{ $game->name }}</p>

{{-- ❌ DON'T - Raw output unless necessary --}}
<p>{!! $game->name !!}</p>

{{-- ✅ OK - When HTML is needed and trusted --}}
<div>{!! $game->sanitized_html_description !!}</div>
```

### SQL Injection Prevention

```php
// ✅ DO - Use Eloquent or query builder
Game::where('name', $name)->get();
DB::table('games')->where('name', $name)->get();

// ✅ DO - Use parameter binding
DB::select('SELECT * FROM games WHERE name = ?', [$name]);

// ❌ DON'T - Concatenate strings
DB::select("SELECT * FROM games WHERE name = '{$name}'");
```

## Performance Standards

### Database Queries

```php
// ✅ DO - Eager load relationships
$games = Game::with('user', 'scores')->get();

// ✅ DO - Select only needed columns
$games = Game::select('id', 'name', 'status')->get();

// ✅ DO - Use chunk for large datasets
Game::chunk(100, function ($games) {
    foreach ($games as $game) {
        // Process
    }
});

// ❌ DON'T - N+1 queries
$games = Game::all();
foreach ($games as $game) {
    echo $game->user->name; // N+1 query
}
```

